rticles and topics related to Joseph Stalin\n| state = collapsed\n| list1 =\n{{Leaders of CPSU}}\n{{USSRpremier}}\n{{Marshals of the Soviet Union}}\n{{Leaders of the Ruling Parties of the Eastern Bloc}}\n{{Cold War}}\n{{Russification}}\n{{Time Persons of the Year|27\u201350}}\n}}\n{{Portal bar|Biography|Communism|Georgia (country)|Politics|Soviet Union}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Stalin, Joseph}}\n[[Category:Joseph Stalin| ]]\n[[Category:1878 births]]\n[[Category:1953 deaths]]\n[[Category:People from Gori, Georgia]]\n[[Category:People from Tiflis Governorate]]\n[[Category:Russian Social Democratic Labour Party members]]\n[[Category:Old Bolsheviks]]\n[[Category:Heads of the Communist Party of the Soviet Union]]\n[[Category:General Secretaries of the Communist Party of the Soviet Union]]\n[[Category:Politburo of the Central Committee of the Communist Party of the Soviet Union members]]\n[[Category:Heads of government of the Soviet Union]]\n[[Category:Soviet Ministers of Defence]]\n[[Category:Generalissimos]]\n[[Category:Marshals of the Soviet Union]]\n[[Category:Soviet Georgian generals]]\n[[Category:Anti-fascists]]\n[[Category:Anti-Polish sentiment]]\n[[Category:Anti-revisionists]]\n[[Category:Antisemitism in Russia]]\n[[Category:Comintern people]]\n[[Category:Communist poets]]\n[[Category:Communists from Georgia (country)]]\n[[Category:Former Georgian Orthodox Christians]]\n[[Category:Great Purge perpetrators]]\n[[Category:Honorary Members of the USSR Academy of Sciences]]\n[[Category:People of the Russian Civil War]]\n[[Category:People of the Russian Revolution]]\n[[Category:People of World War II from Georgia (country)]]\n[[Category:19th-century poets from Georgia (country)]]\n[[Category:Politicians from Georgia (country)]]\n[[Category:Russian exiles]]\n[[Category:Heroes of the Soviet Union]]\n[[Category:Heroes of Socialist Labour]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the Order of Victory]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the Order of the Red Banner]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the Order of Lenin]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the Order of Suvorov, 1st class]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the Order of Sukhbaatar]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the Czechoslovak War Cross]]\n[[Category:Collars of the Order of the White Lion]]\n[[Category:Smallpox survivors]]\n[[Category:Soviet people of World War II]]\n[[Category:World War II political leaders]]\n[[Category:Burials at the Kremlin Wall Necropolis]]\n[[Category:Russian atheism activists]]\n[[Category:Atheists from Georgia (country)]]\n[[Category:People of the Polish\u2013Soviet War]]\n[[Category:Russian revolutionaries]]\n[[Category:Russian communists]]\n[[Category:Russian anti-capitalists]]\n[[Category:Russian political writers]]\n[[Category:Communist rulers]]\n[[Category:Communist writers]]\n[[Category:Genocide perpetrators]]\n[[Category:Stalinism]]\n[[Category:People of the Cold War]]\n[[Category:Soviet politicians]]\n[[Category:Communism in Russia]]\n[[Category:20th-century poets from Georgia (country)]]\n[[Category:Male poets from Georgia (country)]]\n[[Category:Anti-imperialism]]\n[[Category:20th-century atheists]]\n[[Category:First convocation members of the Verkhovna Rada of the Ukrainian Soviet Socialist Republic]]\n[[Category:Deaths from cerebrovascular disease]]\n[[Category:Politicide perpetrators]]\n[[Category:People who died in office]]\n[[Category:Unsolved deaths]]\n", "text_old": "{{Redirect|Stalin}}\n{{pp-semi-indef}}\n{{pp-move-indef}}\n{{short description|Leader of the Soviet Union from 1924 to 1953}}\n{{good article}}\n{{Eastern Slavic name|Vissarionovich|Stalin}}\n{{Use British English|date = March 2020}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=January 2020}}\n{{Infobox officeholder\n| name                = Joseph Stalin\n| native_name         = {{native name|ru|\u0418\u043e\u0441\u0438\u0444 \u0421\u0442\u0430\u043b\u0438\u043d|italics=no}}<br />{{native name|ka|\u10d8\u10dd\u10e1\u10d4\u10d1 \u10e1\u10e2\u10d0\u10da\u10d8\u10dc\u10d8|italics=no}}\n| nickname            = Koba\n| image   